Hoplite is an open source web application that allows you to backup your network devices via an easy to use web interface. This is an alpha and will be changing rapidly.

I will try and update as often as I can, if you have any questions do not hesitate to email me at joshua.pasqualetto at gmail.com


rake db:seed currently provides defaults for the following tested Hardware (Chances are many, many switchs, routers and load balancers are covered however):

Foundry FastIron Edge 4802 - Premium (03.4 FW)
